(1623,101,'service_area_note','<p><strong>Serving Davie Since 2005</strong></p>\n\n<p>We provide comprehensive HVAC service throughout Davie, from rural horse properties to modern residential communities. Our technicians understand the unique needs of western Broward properties, including homes with pole barns, workshops, and specialty cooling requirements.</p>\n\n<p>Same-day service available. 24/7 emergency repairs throughout western Broward County.</p>'),
