r major repairs (compressors, coils, refrigerant leaks). We provide transparent upfront pricing before any work begins, with no hidden fees or surprises.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:54:\"Do you offer emergency AC repair in Light House Point?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:330:\"Yes! We provide 24/7 emergency AC repair throughout Light House Point and surrounding areas. We understand that AC failures don\'t wait for business hours, especially during South Florida\'s brutal summer heat. Our experienced technicians respond quickly to restore your comfort, with most emergency calls answered within 1-2 hours.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:50:\"How long does AC repair take in Light House Point?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:267:\"Most Light House Point AC repairs take 1-3 hours depending on the issue. Simple fixes like thermostat or capacitor replacements take under an hour, while refrigerant leaks or compressor work may take 2-4 hours. We provide accurate time estimates before starting work.\";}i:7;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:57:\"Why choose Sunnyside AC for service in Light House Point?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:300:\"Our technicians know Light House Point\'s unique HVAC challenges including waterfront properties and Intracoastal exposure. We\'re licensed, insured, and factory-trained on all major brands. We provide upfront pricing, same-day service, and 24/7 emergency repairs. Local expertise makes the difference.\";}}'),
