(1957,121,'city_faqs','a:8:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:48:\"What makes HVAC service in Wellington different?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:297:\"Wellington presents unique HVAC challenges due to equestrian estates and western heat. The lack of ocean breezes means AC systems work harder and require more frequent service. Our technicians understand these local conditions and provide service tailored to Wellington\'s specific climate demands.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:47:\"How often should I service my AC in Wellington?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:286:\"In Wellington\'s demanding climate, we recommend AC maintenance at least twice annuallyspring (before peak summer) and fall. The continuous operation and extreme heat require frequent professional inspection. Regular maintenance prevents breakdowns during Wellington\'s hottest months.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:47:\"What AC problems are most common in Wellington?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:263:\"Wellington AC systems commonly experience refrigerant leaks, clogged condensate drains from high humidity, frozen coils from continuous operation, and electrical failures from frequent cycling. Our technicians are experienced with all common Wellington AC issues.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:38:\"What areas of Wellington do you serve?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:256:\"We provide comprehensive HVAC service throughout all Wellington neighborhoods and surrounding areas. We serve both residential neighborhoods and commercial areas throughout the city. Fast response times and same-day service available throughout Wellington.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:43:\"How much does AC repair cost in Wellington?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:284:\"Wellington AC repair costs typically range from $150-$500 for minor repairs (thermostats, capacitors, electrical) to $500-$2,500 for major repairs (compressors, coils, refrigerant leaks). We provide transparent upfront pricing before any work begins, with no hidden fees or surprises.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:47:\"Do you offer emergency AC repair in Wellington?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:323:\"Yes! We provide 24/7 emergency AC repair throughout Wellington and surrounding areas. We understand that AC failures don\'t wait for business hours, especially during South Florida\'s brutal summer heat. Our experienced technicians respond quickly to restore your comfort, with most emergency calls answered within 1-2 hours.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:43:\"How long does AC repair take in Wellington?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:260:\"Most Wellington AC repairs take 1-3 hours depending on the issue. Simple fixes like thermostat or capacitor replacements take under an hour, while refrigerant leaks or compressor work may take 2-4 hours. We provide accurate time estimates before starting work.\";}i:7;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:50:\"Why choose Sunnyside AC for service in Wellington?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:281:\"Our technicians know Wellington\'s unique HVAC challenges including equestrian estates and western heat. We\'re licensed, insured, and factory-trained on all major brands. We provide upfront pricing, same-day service, and 24/7 emergency repairs. Local expertise makes the difference.\";}}'),
